OK, ok, sorry, sorry.

* The shields on the CF were starting to fluctuate, the ship in such 
shambles from the last battle that power wasn't in as much of a supply as it 
was before.
But with all programming pulling in on defences, the fluctuating ceased,for 
now.
There was heavy damage on the shields though, and no one could know for sure 
how long they would last.
Behind the portable shields the autoguns fired away, but more rapidly then 
ever before, steamed on by IRs internal targeting systems.
All three aimed towards Imprisoner, charges sent from all around bouncing 
helplessly off the shields...only being absorbed and adding to the power. 9 
shots were sent all together towards the enemy, all three turning at the 
same time and aiming, this time, at Predator, 5 charges.
But seconds later, they turned towards Choran and fored 12 charges, 8 
disabling 8 laser bolts sent towards Prowl, explosins igniting in the air.*
